Package com.jcabi.simpledb Description

Amazon SimpleDB Object Layer.

The only dependency you need is (check our latest version available at www.jcabi.com): 

<depedency>
   <groupId>com.jcabi</groupId>
   <artifactId>jcabi-simpledb</artifactId>
 </dependency>
